#: ../../6-Good dfc29906c00440eaa0dad4f6fdbaa991 practices.rst:9
msgid ""
"While it is clear that a large number of languages in the world require "
"intensive investment in resource creation for technology enablement, it "
"seems highly unlikely that such an investment can be delivered readily "
"and easily in a short span of time. Given these limited resources, "
"language communities should be empowered to determine the future of their"
" languages. In this document, we have presented how digital "
"representation is part of this process."
msgstr ""

